content: Could somebody please finally fix that issue which keeps resetting login data with updates ffs..?! There is still some space for improvements - e.g. I'm missing a report of triggered alarm, IMHO, one of the best example of usefulness of a mobile connected car. They even added the missing features which were in the previous app and not in this one yet.

content: Skvělá appka, mě funguje naprosto perfektně více jak půl roku, nezaznamenal jsem žádné problémy zmiňované v negativních recenzích. Používám mnohokrát denně např. pro zaslání cíle navigace (ale vyhledání cíle provádím mnohem jednodušeji např. v Google maps a pak nasdílím to této app a z ní odešlu do auta). Doporučil bych vylepšit vyhledávání hlavně hlasové přímo v appce, ať nemusím dělat kroky navíc napřed v Google maps, ale je to celkem detail.
content_english: Great app, it's worked perfectly for me for over six months, I haven’t experienced any of the problems mentioned in the negative reviews. I use it multiple times a day, for example, to send navigation destinations (but I find it much easier to search for destinations, for example, in Google Maps, then I share them with this app and send them to the car). I would suggest improving the search, especially voice search, directly in the app, so I don’t have to take extra steps first in Google Maps, but it’s quite a detail.

A car for 1.4 million. What to do with that?!

content: Num modelo mais antigo de 2015 (série 4) permite atualizar a localização do carro e num modelo novo (X4), não permite e é necessário enviar um comando remoto para atualizar. Isto não faz nenhum sentido e nunca é corrigido nas atualizações. A última atualização de software do carro, que demora o seu tempo a fazer e que causa algum incómodo até estar completa, não altera nada no OS7 num X4 M40i. Não se trata de um sistema operativo antigo, até porque continua a ser instalado em modelos à venda.
content_english: In an older 2015 model (series 4) it allows updating the car's location, and in a newer model (X4) it doesn’t allow it, and it’s necessary to send a remote command to update. This makes no sense and is never corrected in the updates. The latest car software update, which takes its time to complete and causes some inconvenience until it's done, changes nothing in the OS7 in an X4 M40i. It’s not an old operating system, especially as it continues to be installed in models for sale.
topics: vehicle status, connectivity, updates, bmw connected ecosystem

content: Fehlermeldung: Wenn das Betriebssystem (Android) in chinesisch eingestellt ist, Zieladresse (auf deutsch) in App einzugeben, zeigt Fehlermeldung Verbindungensfehler, versuchen noch mal. " In deutsch funktioniert. BMW Connected"- Fenster, Schiebedach, Alarm, Seitenspiegel können nicht durch App steuert werden. - Leider hat das App keine Fahrtenbuch Funktion wie "VOLVO on Call". - Die Außentemperatur vom Auto soll gezeigt werden.
replyContent: Hi! Anderen Nutzern hat es geholfen die OAP Apps direkt im Fahrzeug via "Apps "-"Installierte Apps" -"Option" -"Update Apps" zu aktualisieren. Sollte das Problem bestehen, melde es über "Feedback senden". Das Schließen der Fenster ist aus Sicherheitsgründen nicht möglich. Deine Anregungen leiten wir an unser Produktteam weiter. - My BMW App Team
content_english: Error message: When the operating system (Android) is set to Chinese, entering a destination address (in German) into the app displays an error message: connection error, try again. Works in German. BMW Connected window, sunroof, alarm, and side mirrors cannot be controlled via the app. - Unfortunately, the app doesn’t have a mileage log function like "VOLVO on Call". - The vehicle's outside temperature should be displayed.

content: 地図からの目的地送信が非常にスムーズで便利。これだけで価値あり。 ただ、最近AlexaからのコールでAmazon musicが再生できない。Alexaは反応するがAmazon musicの再生が始まるはずの場面で、My BMWアプリがクラッシュして停止、車両からのアプリ接続が切れるため再生されない。早期改善してほしい。 他、日本では車両自体がホットスポットにならないので、AppとのWifi接続がインターネット接続なし判定になり、毎回接続が面倒。
content_english: Sending destinations from the map is incredibly smooth and convenient. That alone is worth it. However, recently, I can’t play Amazon Music from Alexa. Alexa responds, but when it should start playing Amazon Music, the My BMW App crashes and stops, and the app connection to the vehicle is severed, preventing playback. I hope for an early improvement. Also, in Japan, the vehicle itself doesn't function as a hotspot, so the App's Wi-Fi connection is judged as having no internet connection, and connecting every time is a hassle.
topics: performance, connectivity, multimedia integration, map/navigation, localization & language

皆様のご連絡について、ありがとうございます！MY BMW APPのバージョン2.9.0にて、車両にOS7以上が入っていれば、「走行」機能が使えるようになります。この機能にて、最近のお出かけの持続期間、燃費消費量、平均速度などの情報について確認できます。
‐MY BMW App Support Team

Even when sharing from Google Maps, I don’t know if the map is accurate because it’s going through this app. Remote Camera, Lock Status, and other status confirmations work fine. March 30th Update: The map display has been restored to its previous usability, so I’m changing the rating."

content: 530eで使用中。 このアプリを使いだしてから、ディスプレイキーの出番がなくなりました。 充電状況や可能走行距離の確認、エアコンの乗車前での設定、目的地の登録や充電設備の検索など便利に使っています。 指紋認証で起動できるのも良い点です。 ただ、燃料の残が満タンにしても満タンマイナス3リッターなのは残念ですね。 施錠が出来るのですから、窓を閉めることもしてほしいです。また、トヨタ車のように施錠や窓が開いていることをメールかプッシュ通知で教えてくれると万全です。
content_english: Using this with my 530e. Since I started using this app, I no longer need the Display Key. I’m using it conveniently to check charging status and possible driving range, set the AC before getting in, register destinations, and search for charging stations. The fingerprint authentication startup is a good point. However, it’s a shame that even when the fuel level is full, it shows as full minus 3 liters. Since it can lock the car, I wish it would also close the windows. Also, it would be perfect if it could notify me via email or push notification when the car is locked or windows are open, like with Toyota cars.
topics: digital key/mobile key, vehicle status, remote controls, charging management, notification management

content: 出発前にあらかじめ目的地を車に送信しておけるので非常に便利です。 旧アプリのBMW remoteが2～3年前からAndroud用が使用不能となってしまい、わざわざIpadから送ってましたが、My BMWに移行してAndroidにも対応となりとても助かりました。使い勝手もBMW remoteより良くなってると思います。 このアプリを使うには、BMW connectedサービスの契約が必要です。
content_english: It's very convenient being able to send the destination to the car in advance before leaving. The old BMW Remote app became unusable for Android users 2-3 years ago, so I had to send it from my iPad, but switching to My BMW App and it now supporting Android has been a great help. I think it's also more user-friendly than BMW Remote. Using this app requires a BMW ConnectedDrive service subscription.
topics: remote controls, trip planning, ui/ux, bmw connected ecosystem

content: Alexaに接続出ません。Amazonに聞いたらAmazonサイト上でスキルの取り扱いが無いとの話。何とかして欲しい。
replyContent: 平素よりご利用いただきありがとうございます。Amazon Alexaのデジタル・アシスタントは、BMW OS7 (Version 11/2020)および Connected Package Professional (SA6C3またはSA6C4) でご利用いただけます。また、BMWで、11/2018生産以降のBMW iDrive (タイル式メインメニュー付き) を搭載しており、オプションでBMW ナビゲーション・システム (SA 606、609、6UN、6UP) が備わっている必要があります。その場合は、カスタマー・サポートが対応致しますので、0120-269-437までご連絡ください。
content_english: “Can’t connect to Alexa. When I asked Amazon, they said there’s no skill available on the Amazon website. Please fix this.”

content: 以前同様に使えるので便利、確かにパスワード忘れてメール送信してもなかなか返信無かったり、旧の車から現在の車に更新するまで、まるっきり使え無いですが15分程で全て完了しました 車両登録出来ない人は、コード受信のタイミングと再送信で送られて来る時のコード（毎回更新されます）が違ってるはずです
content_english: Just like before, it's convenient when it works. Certainly, when I forgot my password, it took a while for the email reply to arrive, and it was completely unusable when updating from my old car to the current one, but everything was completed in about 15 minutes. People who can’t register their vehicle – the code you receive (which is updated each time) is likely different from the timing of reception and resending.
